    %h1 Who are we?

    %p.body-text
      WEST, Inc. was founded in 1990 by its two principals, Dr. Dale Strickland and Dr. Lyman McDonald. Since then, WEST has grown to be one of the premier environmental and statistical consulting firms in the United States, and over the years has included Projects spanning North and South AmericaIn 2017 WEST, ULC was founded with the same core values and principles as our US parent company.

